  protein: 50 g
  fiber: 11 g
  sodium: 1990 mg
cuisine: Indian
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spicy-chicken-coconut-curry-soup-64d3d325b7c13e5fd9fd1fc4
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
